http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Power-cut-forces-BU-to-postpone-exam/article14011825.ece

Low visibility in an exam hall caused by a power cut coupled with the gloomy weather forced Bangalore University (BU) to postpone the supplementary exam for final year BA History students under the distance and correspondence education scheme.Ningegowda K.N., Registrar (Evaluation), BU, said there was a power cut around 4.20 p.m. while the exam was underway in the Central College campus. “We waited till 5.20 p.m. and then decided to hold a re-exam. We will announce a new date soon,” he said.Power supply was restored around 5.50 p.m.